tag-medina","tag-muhammad","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi","tag-swords-sayf"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-15m","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":8100,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/prophet-humble-young-servants\/","url_meta":{"origin":4176,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Humility: The Prophet is humble with young servants","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: Any of the young servant-girls among the people of Medina would take the hand of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and lead him wherever she wished. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6072 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0646\u0633 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0627\u0644\u0643 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1872,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/01\/21\/hadith-on-medina\/","url_meta":{"origin":4176,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Medina: The Prophet&#8217;s city expels impurity like a furnace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported:\u00a0A bedouin came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and gave the pledge of allegiance for embracing Islam. The next day he came with a fever and he said, \u201cCancel my pledge.\u201d The Prophet refused three times and he said, \u201cMedina is like a furnace. It\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/10\/15\/prophet-loves-al-madinah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4176,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Madinah: The Prophet loves his city Medina","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, returned from a journey and saw the walls of Medina from afar, he would quicken his pace and, if he was on an animal, he would make it gallop out of his love for Medina. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7292,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/madinah-rejoice-coming-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":4176,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Madinah: People of Medina rejoice at arrival of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, arrived in Medina, the Abyssinians began playing, rejoicing at his arrival, and they played with their spears. Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4923 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u062f\u0650\u0645\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2921,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/16\/prophet-abu-bakr-cave-hijrah\/","url_meta":{"origin":4176,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Tawakkul: The Prophet and Abu Bakr trust Allah in the cave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakr reported: I saw the feet of the idolaters over our heads while we were hiding in the cave, fleeing to Medina. I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, if one of them only looked under his feet, he would see us!\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7672,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/dua-prophet-rain-miracle\/","url_meta":{"origin":4176,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Miracles: The Prophet prays for rain, it rains","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, on Friday while he was delivering a sermon in Medina. The man said, \u201cThere is no rain, so please call upon your Lord to bless us with rain.\u201d The Prophet looked at the sky\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4176","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4176"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4176\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4176"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4176"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4176"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}